Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是庆树岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里其实是法芙娜的机库
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要来了 小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思维会被它侵蚀的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果回答了 人类就会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体 不听使唤…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 去感受法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和它融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它看穿了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在能用的只有电磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻装进飞龙的弹射器
