Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.88,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：俗译林德虫 欧洲传说中的有翼龙或大海蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚瑠岛的跑道不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从这里直接扎进那家伙体内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算装到飞龙的弹射器上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里也没法控制发射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你背后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 它打算同化你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把它甩开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,止痛机能启动
