Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须一击就把敌人解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
