Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚瑠岛包括一部分跑道在内的第二次装备全毁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损失惨重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三栋房屋被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失踪人数目前为28 但已确认到其中二人的生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向岛迎击系统全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…我们的岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲…战死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令代为指挥的战斗 你认为如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为 那是当时的最佳选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你指挥的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设的情境我无意奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今后准备怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要在这儿站多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先失陪了 我还有分析敌人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况应该早就在意料之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 今晚一定要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来 还有这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去问你爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他…也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 伤患还多着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去叫真壁叔叔来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 再给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想他应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天能来上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 进屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 今晚一定要好好休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 远见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西你从哪捡回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的什么话 这是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家…在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得让他努力才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我们家叫「春日井」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是孩子就是纽带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.90,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：春日井和纽带同音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爸你好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人是纽带？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连灯都不开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸 你爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（part-b）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶那东西的感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定吃惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的人们居然在干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 如果我说日本已经不存在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 日本…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是29年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京呢 大阪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛就已经从地图上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是觉得难以置信？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这种东西就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到昨天为止 唯有这个岛才是乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能得救 是多亏了校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是多亏了你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们还会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会和我一起战斗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你特地过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于一骑的身体 有些话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有教工会议所以回来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你还想骗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…你生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生给了我这套衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你今天不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想想要是没有我 你连饭都不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸我以前也是自己做饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是结婚之前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 今晚我来露一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西 我已经在今天失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 待在这里我更平静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才聊的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是假设是我指挥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换成是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是皆城…前司令把你分配到CDC的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 不赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这米你都没洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的事 你都知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别问我为什么要瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和总士一起战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见医生都跟你说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 法芙娜的训练就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于一骑的身体 有些话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记录显示 他在驾驶中的意识和平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…战斗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的染色体出现了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不能断定 需要观察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过继续这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:19:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红音 对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏前原来是机器人的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她才没和我们一起去避难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏前她去战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 爸爸不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个机器人我也能开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没开玩笑吧 搞不好会没命的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 一骑去开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城和一骑最近好像经常去地下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 我也想一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哪个一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑他好像很努力的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 把衣服全脱了然后走过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 全脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放进后面的洗衣柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你回来的时候就洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是杀菌灯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两眼直视前方走过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 从我这里看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 又要痛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上这套协同作用服就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协同作…用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会痛嘛
